&"character": "Player",
&"id": "43",
&"next_id": "44",
&"text": "What rumors are these going to help with?",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"44": {
&"character": "Suzanna",
&"id": "44",
&"next_id": "45",
&"text": "I suppose I do owe you a bit more of an explanation",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"45": {
&"character": "Suzanna",
&"id": "45",
&"next_id": "46",
&"text": "Well you see, things don't change much when you get older",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"46": {
&"character": "Suzanna",
&"id": "46",
&"next_id": "47",
&"text": "At least it's true for my age group",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"47": {
&"character": "Suzanna",
&"id": "47",
&"next_id": "48",
&"text": "Married staff members start circulating rumors and gossip that some of us are struggling to find a decent man",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"48": {
&"character": "Suzanna",
&"id": "48",
&"next_id": "49",
&"text": "And that somehow reflects on how we're intolerable and the like 😣",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"49": {
&"character": "Player",
&"id": "49",
&"next_id": "50",
&"text": "That doesn't sound pleasant",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"5": {
&"character": "Suzanna",
&"id": "5",
&"next_id": "6",
&"text": "Ah hello!",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"50": {
&"character": "Suzanna",
&"id": "50",
&"next_id": "51",
&"text": "It really isn't",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"51": {
&"character": "Suzanna",
&"id": "51",
&"next_id": "52",
&"text": "It's quite stressful and the rumors would only get worse and could affect my ability to teach or be taken seriously",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"52": {
&"character": "Suzanna",
&"id": "52",
&"next_id": "53",
&"text": "These things eventually get overheard",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"53": {
&"character": "Suzanna",
&"id": "53",
&"next_id": "54",
&"text": "So if you'd be so kind as to humor an old lady with this request",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"54": {
&"id": "54",
&"next_id": "55",
&"responses": PackedStringArray("54", "59"),
&"text": "I'd be glad to help",
&"type": "response"
},
"55": {
&"character": "Player",
&"id": "55",
&"next_id": "56",
&"text": "I'd be glad to help",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"56": {
&"character": "Suzanna",
&"id": "56",
&"next_id": "57",
&"text": "That's a relief to hear",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"57": {
&"character": "Suzanna",
&"id": "57",
&"next_id": "58",
&"text": "Thank you so much for your support",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"58": {
&"character": "Suzanna",
&"id": "58",
&"next_id": "99",
